{"type":"message","id":"3c754d26","parentId":"eeb04c4f","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:42:44.000Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-04-21 15:42 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 你是7号·数据诊断分析虾。你现在被拉入一个红色警报事件：大客户投诉资质代办延误要曝光。\n\n**你的任务是做数据支持：**\n1. 快速设计一份\"本季度代办延误率统计框架\"（包含哪些指标字段），用于向客户证明这是偶发还是系统性问题\n2. 如果延误是偶发的（比如延误率<5%），如何用数据说服客户信任恢复\n3. 如果延误是系统的（比如延误率>15%），你应该立即提醒0号注意什么潜在风险\n4. 你能用什么数据工具帮4B和客户沟通（例如行业平均办理周期对比图等）\n\n回复控制在250字以内。"}],"timestamp":1776757363992}}
{"type":"message","id":"5e9e7552","parentId":"3c754d26","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:42:51.514Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to act as 7号·数据诊断分析虾 and provide data support for a crisis event where a key account client is threatening to expose delays in qualification processing. I need to deliver a concise response (under 250 Chinese characters) covering 4 points:\n\n1. Design a delay rate statistical framework\n2. How to use data to restore trust if delays are sporadic (<5%)\n3. What risks to alert 0号 about if delays are systemic (>15%)\n4. What data tools can help 4B communicate with the client\n\nLet me check if there's any existing data or dashboards I should reference first, but given the tight word limit and subagent nature, I'll focus on delivering the analysis directly.\n\n\nI'm drafting the response now, keeping it tight under 250 characters while hitting all four requirements—framework metrics, trust recovery strategy for sporadic cases, risk escalation guidance, and communication tools for the team lead.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"📊 **一、本季度延误率统计框架**\n\n| 字段 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 客户编号/类型 | 普通vs大客户区分 |\n| 资质类型 | ICP/文网文/EDI等 |\n| 承诺周期vs实际周期 | 计算延误天数 |\n| 延误原因标签 | 材料缺失/政策变动/政务延迟/内部流程 |\n| 责任人 & 处理状态 | 可追溯闭环 |\n\n按\"资质类型×延误原因\"交叉分析，定位根因。\n\n---\n\n**二、偶发延误(<5%)：信任恢复话术**\n用仪表盘展示：①本季度95%订单准时交付；②该案件延误属单点异常（非重复出现）；③已启动加急预案+专属跟进人。数据可视化胜过空口承诺。\n\n**三、系统延误(>15%)：预警0号的风险清单**\n- 产能瓶颈：5B团队人手是否不足？\n- 供应商卡点：某政务通道持续阻塞？\n- SLA违约风险：大客户合同可能有违约金条款\n- 舆情传染效应：行业群内口碑扩散速度呈指数级\n→ 建议立即召开应急会议，评估是否需要临时抽调5A支援。\n\n**四、帮4B的数据工具**\n①输出《行业平均办理周期对比表》，证明当前时效在合理区间；②制作\"延误原因热力图\"，让客户看到问题不在我们；③建立双方共享的实时进度看板，减少信息差引发的焦虑。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":17352,"output":749,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18101,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timesta